<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p> They celebrated the show's 10th anniversary on Sunday.</p>

<p>And the cast of TOWIE were out in force in Essex on Tuesday as they filmed scenes for the brand new series. </p>

<p>Chloe Sims, 37, led the pack as she made a head-turning arrival in a busty black cut-out top and leather jacket, while Courtney Green, 25, looked stylish in a beige co-ord. </p>

