<p> She added to her safari look with tan suede boots and a Louis Vuitton clutch bag. </p>

<p>Chloe looked every inch the show veteran as she strutted through a car park with her sisters Demi, 23, and Frankie, 25, who have only joined TOWIE in recent years. </p>

